overview:
Knead Entertainment Group is a Denver, CO-based, full-service entertainment industry services company–dedicated to bringing the world of art back to the artists. We specialize in developing and promoting artists’ careers through artist-business creation and development, as well as innovative marketing solutions–designed with today’s entertainment industry in mind.

We offer a wide array of services from media production, placement and distribution, to brand development, promotion, and full-service business development. Our services are completely customizable, and although we specialize in working with artists, many of our marketing solutions have proven to be great tools for all businesses! Along with the ongoing tally of artists that we have worked with–both local and abroad, KEG has provided services for businesses such as Record Labels, Concert Venues, Print Media and even Construction Contractors.

Contact Us for a free One Hour consultation–where we will sit down together and all of us assess the current stage of your career and begin forming a plan to give your career direction.
